These rom&nd tints are the perfect mix of hydration and pigment! ✨

Here’s my take on each shade:

💖 Pink Pumpkin – A warm, muted pink that flatters all skin tones. It’s the perfect MLBB shade for a soft, everyday look.

🍫 Dark Coconut – A rich, deep brick-brown with a hint of red. Ideal for that bold yet wearable vibe.

🍇 Bare Grape – A cool-toned mauve with a sheer, glossy finish. It gives that effortless, just-bitten look.

✔️ Formula: Super lightweight, non-sticky, and gives a juicy, glass-like shine.
✔️ Pigment: Buildable and long-lasting, fades into a soft stain.
✔️ Verdict: Hydrating and comfortable—zero dryness! These are perfect if you love glossy tints that last.
